Invocation Name: rezility
des:
Discover personalized opportunities, useful services and local fun, every day!
Favorite a feed to read later at your convenience and follow an organization.
Discover people, places and what’s new around you — whether at home, at work or in the community.
Identify opportunities in your virtual neighborhood, and helpful services where you are or where you plan to be.

Listed below are a few ways our skill for Rezility will help you out. But don’t be restricted by this list, there is a plethora of search options for abundant requirements!

Here are a few utterances to help you get started:
1. Alexa, open/launch Rezility. 
2. Alexa, ask Rezility to get nearby properties.
3. Alexa, ask Rezility to get me some feeds.
4. Alexa, ask Rezility to tell me about Financial Counseling.
